@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}
<main aria-labelledby="title">
    <h2 id="title" class="page-title">@ViewBag.Title</h2>

    <section class="introduction">
        <p>
            Welcome to <strong>iCARE Healthcare System</strong>, a modern healthcare management platform designed to streamline workflows and improve patient care. Our system is built to empower doctors and nurses by providing an efficient way to manage patient information, track treatment records, and coordinate care—all from one user-friendly interface.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <h4>What You Can Do with iCARE:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>View and manage your active patient lists.</li>
            <li>Assign yourself to patients with ease.</li>
            <li>Access and update essential documents, including patient and treatment records, in real time.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mission">
        <h4>Our Mission</h4>
        <p>
            At iCARE, we strive to enhance workplace efficiency, enabling healthcare professionals to focus on what matters most—providing exceptional patient care.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="story">
        <h4>Our Story</h4>
        <p>
            <strong>iCARE Healthcare System</strong> was founded by a dedicated team of five visionary women:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Kenzie McAllister</li>
            <li>Gabi Ramirez</li>
            <li>Sophia Martin</li>
            <li>Jessica Xie</li>
            <li>Neela Hanumanthiah</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            Based in <strong>Columbia, Missouri</strong>, we are passionate about creating technology that bridges gaps in healthcare delivery. Our journey began with a shared belief that every healthcare worker deserves tools that make their jobs easier while fostering better patient outcomes.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="vision">
        <h4>Our Vision</h4>
        <p>
            We are committed to advancing healthcare through innovation. Our goal is to expand iCARE and deliver cutting-edge solutions to healthcare systems across the nation. Together, we aim to redefine what’s possible in patient care.
        </p>
    </section>

    <footer class="closing">
        <p>
            Thank you for choosing <strong>iCARE Healthcare System</strong>—where compassionate care meets innovation.
        </p>
    </footer>
</main>
